                <span class="feature-icon">üìã</span>
                <span><strong>Reservation Management:</strong> View, modify, and manage guest reservations and waitlists</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üë•</span>
                <span><strong>Guest Relations:</strong> Access guest preferences, special requests, and dining history</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üì±</span>
                <span><strong>Real-time Updates:</strong> Get instant notifications about arrivals, delays, and special needs</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if (eq role 'server')}}
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üçΩÔ∏è</span>
                <span><strong>Order Management:</strong> View pre-orders, dietary restrictions, and special requests</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üí≥</span>
                <span><strong>Payment Handling:</strong> Process additional orders, modifications, and gratuities</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">‚≠ê</span>
                <span><strong>Guest Experience:</strong> Access loyalty status, preferences, and personalized recommendations</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if (eq role 'kitchen')}}
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üë®‚Äçüç≥</span>
                <span><strong>Kitchen Display:</strong> Real-time order queue with timing and special instructions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">‚è±Ô∏è</span>
                <span><strong>Timing Control:</strong> Hold, fire, and mark orders ready with ETA tracking</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üîÑ</span>
                <span><strong>Order Modifications:</strong> Handle last-minute changes and dietary accommodations</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if (eq role 'manager')}}
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üìä</span>
                <span><strong>Analytics Dashboard:</strong> Revenue, covers, timing metrics, and guest satisfaction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üë•</span>
                <span><strong>Staff Management:</strong> Invite team members, assign roles, and manage permissions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</span>
                <span><strong>Restaurant Settings:</strong> Manage menus, availability, pricing, and operational hours</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="feature-item">
                <span class="feature-icon">üìû</span>
                <span><strong>Support Access:</strong> Direct line to La Carta support for any technical issues</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>The La Carta platform is designed to help you deliver exceptional experiences while streamlining operations. Everything is integrated ‚Äì from reservations to payments to kitchen timing ‚Äì so you can focus on what you do best: hospitality.</p>

        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
        <ol style="padding-left: 20px; color: #374151;">
            <li>Click the login button above to access your staff portal</li>
            <li>Change your temporary password to something secure</li>
            <li>Complete your staff profile with your preferences and availability</li>
            <li>Explore the training materials and feature guides</li>
            <li>Reach out to your manager or our support team with any questions</li>
        </ol>

        <p>We're here to support you every step of the way. Welcome to the future of restaurant operations!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Welcome aboard,<br>The La Carta Team</p>
            <p style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>{{restaurantName}}</strong><br>
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none;">Staff Portal</a> ‚Ä¢ 
                <a href="{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none;">Support</a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px;">
                ¬© {{year}} La Carta. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>